      *----------------------------------------------------*
     CSR         $SB500    BEGSR
      *
      **
     C                     MOVEL@TOKU     P@TOKU  4
     C                     MOVEL@NONY     P@NONY  4
     C                     MOVEL@NKOJ     P@NKOJ  1
     C                     MOVEL@NUKE     P@NUKE  4
     C                     MOVEL@YYYY     P@YYYY  4
     C                     MOVEL@MMMM     P@MMMM  2
     C                     MOVEL@SIZI     P@SIZI  1
JW1  C                     MOVEL@TYPE     P@TYPE  1
      *                    MOVEL@TANK     P@TANK  1
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    P@STS   1
     C                     CALL 'MBDRT4'
     C                     PARM           P@TOKU
     C                     PARM           P@NONY
     C                     PARM           P@NKOJ
     C                     PARM           P@NUKE
     C                     PARM           P@YYYY
     C                     PARM           P@MMMM
     C                     PARM           P@SIZI
JW1  C                     PARM           P@TYPE
