** ERR
E-01 YEAR IS WRONG.
E-02 MONTH IS WRONG.
E-03 YEAR AND MONTH IS WRONG.
E-04 NO DATA.
E-05 REQUIRED
E-06 ENTER E-MAIL ADDRESS
E-07 ENTER TYPE 1 OR 2.
